<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Management System</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background: linear-gradient(to right, #00008b, #add8e6);
    }

    .header {
      background-color: #333; 
      color: #fff; 
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .content {
      position: relative;
      height: 100vh; 
      overflow: hidden; 
    }

    .background-image {
      position: absolute;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      height: 100%;
      background-image: url('https://buzzflick.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/01/social-media-animation-768x356.png');
      background-size: cover;
      background-position: center;
      filter: brightness(50%); 
    }

    .text-section {
      position: absolute;
      bottom: 0;
      left: 0;
      width: 100%;
      background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8); 
      padding: 20px;
      text-align: center;
    }

    h1 {
      color: #007bff; 
      margin-bottom: 10px;
    }

    p {
      color: #6c757d; 
      font-size: 18px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>


  <div class="content">
    <div class="background-image"></div>
    <div class="text-section">
      <h2>Welcome to Fakebook</h2>
      <p>Welcome to the social network for everyone. Connect with friends, share updates, and discover what's happening in the world.</p>
      <p>Join us today and start connecting!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>


